{
  "texts": [
    "We also tried an alternative remix operation proposed by Ref. 39.",
    "It introduces a remix operation in latent space that combines multiple cases to create new learning inputs and targets.",
    "This approach differs from our SoftMix operation, which mixes information within a single case while maintaining the same target.",
    "As shown in Table 5, with the remixmatch component the model performs poorly on textual tasks.",
    "This observation aligns with the previous findings at: https://github.com/microsoft/Semi-supervised-learning/ blob/main/results/usb_nlp.csv."
  ]
}